title: Next Car Game Technology Sneak Peek 2.0 (Pre-Order Exclusive)
description:
The Free Technology Demo contains a limited version of the playground scene that we use internally to test various features like car damage and environment destruction. Note that this sneak peek does not represent the gameplay and quality of the final game. In the final game the action will take place on many locations including a number of race tracks and derby arenas.

By pre-ordering Next Car Game, you'll get instant access to play Early Access version and Technology Sneak Peek 2.0, featuring more awesome content like like 24 car battles, physics cannon with missiles, new destructive machinery, more spectacular stunts and a ton of dynamic stuff to blow up!
